    "The reason for this is that the public keys of the validators are stored in the blocks.",
    "The public keys of the validators are used for proof in the authorization process.",
    "The PoA mechanism is followed by the PoS mechanism.",
    "The PoW mechanism provides the best result in terms of block size.",
    "As seen in the last row of Table 2, it shows approximately 4% better results than POA and approximately 1% better results than POS for sensitive data."
